Game reference data in src/game/genshin/data.generated.json is derived from the
genshin-db project (https://github.com/theBowja/genshin-db) at build time.
Genshin Impact and all related data are property of HoYoverse. This project bundles
only numeric stat/reference data for interoperability; no game assets are included.
Data snapshot: patch (see "patch" field in data.generated.json).

## Meta build recipes

The "meta build" recipes in `src/meta/metaTargets.ts` (recommended set, main stats,
and stat targets per character) are hand-adapted from the community guides at
KQM (KeqingMains, https://keqingmains.com). They are summaries of public guidance,
not copied text, and are used as an optional, overridable comparison target. Genshin
Impact and all related data are property of HoYoverse.

## Weapon rankings, talent targets, and team comps

The curated weapon rankings (`src/meta/weapons.ts`), talent priority/targets
(`src/meta/talents.ts`), and team comps (`src/meta/teamComps.ts`) are likewise
hand-adapted summaries of public guidance from KQM (KeqingMains,
https://keqingmains.com), used as optional, overridable recommendations
filtered by the player's own account. Genshin Impact and all related data are
property of HoYoverse.
